### Organized Storage

```
Study Library
|
|-- Machine Learning
|   |-- Notes
|   |-- Summaries
|   |-- Quiz History
|
|-- Statistics
|   |-- Notes
|   |-- Summaries
|   |-- Quiz History
```

### Features

* Add Notes
* Edit Notes
* Delete Notes
* Search
* Filter by Subject
