### Basic Details

```
Name
Role
(Student / Professional)
Education Level
```

### Productivity Profile

```
Average Focus Time
Preferred Study Time
```

Options:

* Morning
* Afternoon
* Evening
* Night

### AI Learning Style

Detect:

* Visual Learner
* Reading Learner
* Practice Learner

Then customize:

* Quiz difficulty
* Summary style
* Study plans

