# Final Product Summary

**NeuroLearn AI** is an AI-powered study planner that helps users:

* Organize subjects and deadlines
* Summarize notes automatically
* Generate quizzes and track performance
* Plan study schedules based on availability
* Improve focus with smart timers
* Store and manage learning resources
* Receive AI-driven reminders and recommendations
* Analyze learning progress through dashboards and reports

This makes NeuroLearn AI more than a study app—it becomes a personalized AI learning coach for students and professionals.